<head>
  <title>
    <%=title%>
  </title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/details.css">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/878d22e054.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="navigate">
    <nav>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Brands</a>
          <div class="sub-menu">
            <ul class="sub-menu">
              <li><a href="/cart/iphone">iphone</a></li>
              <li><a href="">samsung</a></li>
              <li><a href="">realme</a></li>
              <li><a href="/cart/oppo">oppo</a></li>
              <li><a href="/cart/vivo">vivo</a></li>
              <li><a href="">oneplus</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="#">Stores</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/users/sign-up" target="_blank"><button type="submit">Sign-Up / Sign-In</button></a></li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/cart/show"><img src="/pic/sc1.png" alt="" class="cart1" width="38" height="40"> </a>
      <div class="countitems">0</div>
      <% if(locals.user){%>
        <a href="/users/profile"><button class="cart2"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%=user.name%>
              </button></a>
        <%} else{%>
          <a href="/users/sign-in"><button class="cart2"><i class="fa-solid fa-user"></i></button></a>
          <%}%>
            <img src="/pic/menu.png" alt="" class="menu-btn" width="40" height="50">
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="card-wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <!-- card left -->
      <div class="product-imgs">
        <div class="img-display">
          <div class="img-showcase">
            <img src="<%=product.imagePath%>" alt="shoe image">
            <img src="shoes_images/shoe_2.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            <img src="shoes_images/shoe_3.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            <img src="shoes_images/shoe_4.jpg" alt="shoe image">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-select">
          <div class="img-item">
            <a href="#" data-id="1">
              <img src="shoes_images/shoe_1.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="img-item">
            <a href="#" data-id="2">
              <img src="shoes_images/shoe_2.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="img-item">
            <a href="#" data-id="3">
              <img src="shoes_images/shoe_3.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="img-item">
            <a href="#" data-id="4">
              <img src="shoes_images/shoe_4.jpg" alt="shoe image">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- card right -->
      <div class="product-content">
        <h2 class="product-title">
          <%=product.desc%>
        </h2>
        <a href="#" class="product-link">visit <%=product.brand%> store</a>
        <div class="product-rating">
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
          <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
          <span>4.7(21)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="product-price">
          <p class="last-price">Old Price: <span>₹ <%=product.mrp%></span></p>
          <p class="new-price">New Price: <span>₹ <%=product.price%> (5%)</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-detail">
          <h2>about this item: </h2>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illo eveniet veniam tempora fuga tenetur placeat
            sapiente architecto illum soluta consequuntur, aspernatur quidem at sequi ipsa!</p>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Consequatur, perferendis eius. Dignissimos, labore
            suscipit. Unde.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Color: <span>Black</span></li>
            <li>Available: <span>in stock</span></li>
            <li>Category: <span>Shoes</span></li>
            <li>Shipping Area: <span>All over the world</span></li>
            <li>Shipping Fee: <span>Free</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="purchase-info">
          <button type="button" class="btn">
            Add to Cart <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="social-links">
          <p>Share At: </p>
          <a href="#">
            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#">
            <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#">
            <i class="fab fa-pinterest"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <script src="/details.js"></script>
</body>